					<ProtectedString name="Source"><![CDATA[--[[				    _____ _                   _
	     	/\         / ____| |                 (_)    
		   /  \ ______| |    | |__   __ _ ___ ___ _ ___ 
		  / /\ \______| |    | '_ \ / _` / __/ __| / __|
